import styled from 'styled-components'
import {OuterContainer, BlogContainer, BlogSmallTitle, BlogBigTitle, BlogCover} from '../components/BlogFolder/BlogPage/BlogElements'

const Blog = () => {
  return (
    <OuterContainer>
      <BlogHeader>
        <HeaderTitles>
          <BlogSmallTitle>My Personal</BlogSmallTitle>
        <BlogBigTitle>Blog</BlogBigTitle>
        </HeaderTitles>
      </BlogHeader>
      
      <BlogCover src={require('../content/img/blog-cover.jpg').default}/>
    </OuterContainer>
  )
}

export default Blog
